Package com.ptc.windchill.contentcontrol.postprocessors

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ContentControlPostProcessor
    Content control post processor specification for to manipulate the ContentControlLinks and ContentControlRelationLinks, created by Content Control Service.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractContentControlPostProcessor
    Non-Concrete implementation Content Control Post processor.
    IndirectionPostProcessor
    Concrete implementation of Content Control Post processor which deals with the indirection content control links created.
    PostProcessorConfiguration
    This class reads and creates in memory structure of Content Control Post Processor configuration.
